monty
=====

[![](https://dev.azure.com/lycantropos/monty/_apis/build/status/lycantropos.monty?branchName=master)](https://dev.azure.com/lycantropos/monty/_build/latest?definitionId=2&branchName=master "Azure Pipelines")
